value.0: A portly older man, the Burgomaster wears serviceable clothing of good quality. His manner is courteous, though somewhat guarded.

A gruff looking woman characterized by quietude; she bears the symbol of Tempus branded into her plate and etched into her cloak. Her face is marred with a scar running diagonal across the right side of her face; her hair is a dirty blonde and her eyes a murky blue.

The Heavy foot of Kohlingen are amongst the finest upon Amia and arguably in the surrounding isles. This fact is highlighted by the skill in which the arms and armor of the Kohlingen infantry are crafted.
